=head1 NAME

libgmsec_perl::ProductFileMessage

	A ProductFileMessage object that is capable of storing ProductFile objects.

	The following message schema IDs and their templates are supported:
	 MSG.PROD.AAA 
	 MSG.PROD.AUTO 
	 MSG.PROD.FD 
	 MSG.PROD.MAS 
	 MSG.PROD.PAS 
	 MSG.PROD.SC 
	 MSG.PROD.TAC 
	 REQ.PROD.AAA 
	 REQ.PROD.AUTO 
	 REQ.PROD.FD 
	 REQ.PROD.MAS 
	 REQ.PROD.PAS 
	 REQ.PROD.SC 
	 REQ.PROD.TAC 
	 RESP.PROD.AAA 
	 RESP.PROD.AUTO 
	 RESP.PROD.FD 
	 RESP.PROD.MAS 
	 RESP.PROD.PAS 
	 RESP.PROD.SC 
	 RESP.PROD.TAC

